project_descr: As followup to Darfur Development Strategy  (DDS), this multi sectoral programme is developed to achieve peace and stability through community based reintegration, security, and arms control in Darfur.

outputs.output_descr: The project aims to strengthen local capacities in conflict mitigation, promote livelihoods for those with conflict carrying capacities, and foster an enabling environment for facilitating resilience and promote graduated arms control and stabilization

document_name: Community Security and Arms Control (CSAC) in Darfur
project_title: darfur community based reintegration and csac - dds
